window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In 1931, Edgar Cayce agreed to help a group of people grow spiritually and become more psychic, with one condition: They would have to live the precepts. It took the group 11 years to apply and compile the 24 lessons that became <i>A Search for God, Books I and II</i>. This material has helped individuals and groups around the world to discover a closer attunement to God. </p>"; 
